                <h3>10. San Francisco</h3>
                <p class="text-justify">San Francisco is one of the top attractions among tourists. The city is trendy for its steeply inclined streets, Victoria architecture, Pacific coastline, and Golden Gate Bridge. The city is extensively known for its liberal atmosphere, LGBTQ communities, sourdough bread, and seafood. </p>

